article_id:3300,category_name:News,title_name:Regarding an Issue With Primal Brunhilda's Dragon Strike,image_path:,message:<div>In chapter 20 quest 7-2 &quot;The Masked Beasts&quot; and chapter 25 quest 3-5 &quot;The Primal Trial&quot;, when using 5â˜… dragon Primal Brunhilda&#39;s dragon strike after defeating a boss and before the next boss appears, some of the treasure chests that drop after defeating the last boss will not open, the result screen will not display, and the game may stop working.</div><div><br></div><div>If this issue occurs, please try to restart the game.</div><div>Note that you will obtain all rewards including the drop rewards normally when clearing these quests even if this issue occurs.</div><div><br></div><div>Any further updates concerning this issue will be posted to this notice.</div><div><br></div><div>Thank you for playing Dragalia Lost.</div>,start_time:1653458400,update_time1653382048